rows.label: qst100303_msg0001
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Getting minced up here not
fit with plans of Pupun!

rows.label: qst100303_msg0002
rows.name:
Pupun have hopes and dreams of
eating world's tasty treats.

rows.label: qst100303_msg0003
rows.name:
Waa... Those eyes looking at
Pupun as if Pupun tasty treat.

rows.label: qst100303_msg0004
rows.name:
Ah! Kind friend who give
Pupun tasty treat!

rows.label: qst100303_msg0101
rows.name:
Thank you, friend. Pupun
about to become tasty treat
of big nasty Vacuum Brogs.

rows.label: qst100303_msg0102
rows.name:
Friend look at Pupun as if to say,
Pupun ungrateful Nopon that not
reward gift of food from friend...

rows.label: qst100303_msg0103
rows.name:
Hey, hey, wait, wait! Don't
say nasty thing... Pupun
not such bad Nopon!

rows.label: qst100303_msg0104
rows.name:
Pupun get all worked up
when at helm of ship...

rows.label: qst100303_msg0105
rows.name:
Pupun go to Invidia now, then
back to Avaritia to give friend
proper token of thank-you.

rows.label: qst100303_msg0106
rows.name:
Pupun manage it this
time! That promise!

rows.label: qst100303_msg0107
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Haha! Get a load of
Pupun's excellent skills!

rows.label: qst100303_msg0108
rows.name:
Hmmm? Helm wiggling
about in funny way...
